message: Hey ladies of Cru, the Lighthouse (416 11th Ave SE) still has 7 spots open for any girls who are interested in living in gospel housing next year! This is such a fantastic opportunity for great community and fellowship with other gals who love Jesus. :) If you are interested in living with us next year, have any questions, or if you know of anyone who might be interested in this opportunity, please feel free to message me or contact me at 612-719-3759. We'd love to have you join us :)
